                <hr>
                <h4 class="title4">Notification</h4>
                <div class="checkbox">
                  <label>
                    <%= check_box_tag :mailchimp, true %>
                Stay informed for all the latest news from Malimar.tv to take your career to where you want it to go. This newsletter includes search tips, cool companies, highlights of new services and much more.
